signed fullback [[Matt Quillen]].\n*'''August 6''' \u2013 Placed wide receiver [[Brennan Marion]] on [[injured reserve]]. and offensive tackle [[SirVincent Rogers]] on the Reserve/Retired list.\n*'''August 10''' \u2013 Waived fullback [[Matt Quillen]] and signed wide receiver [[James Robinson (gridiron football)|James Robinson]] and placekicker [[Connor Barth]].\n*'''August 11''' \u2013 Signed fullback [[Joe Kowalewski]].\n*'''August 12''' \u2013 Placed safety [[Ethan Kilmer]] on the Commissioner's Exemption list.\n*'''August 19''' \u2013 Released cornerback [[Eric Green (cornerback)|Eric Green]].\n*'''August 19''' \u2013 Moved safety [[Ethan Kilmer]] to the Reserve/Left Squad list.\n*'''August 24''' \u2013 Waived running back [[Anthony Kimble]], nose tackle [[Joe Cohen]], linebacker [[Tearrius George]] and linebacker [[Orion Martin]].\n*'''August 24''' \u2013 Waived/injured wide receiver [[Chris Williams (wide receiver)|Chris Williams]].\n*'''August 24''' \u2013 Traded offensive lineman [[Andy Alleman]] and [[Ikechuku Ndukwe]] to the [[Kansas City Chiefs]] in exchange for an undisclosed [[2010 NFL Draft]] pick.\n*'''August 25''' \u2013 Released wide receiver [[Chris Williams (wide receiver)|Chris Williams]] with an injury settlement.\n*'''August 29''' \u2013 Waived wide receiver [[Anthony Armstrong (American football)|Anthony Armstrong]], nose tackle [[Louis Ellis]] and placekicker [[Connor Barth]].\n*'''August 29''' \u2013 Waived/injured fullback [[Joe Kowalewski]].\n*'''September 1''' \u2013 Placed fullback [[Joe Kowalewski]] on [[injured reserve]].\n*'''September 5''' \u2013 Waived or released safety [[Courtney Bryan]], offensive tackle [[Brandon Frye]], linebacker [[William Kershaw]], wide receiver [[Brandon London]], cornerback [[Joey Thomas]], defensive end [[Rodrique Wright]], offensive tackle [[Nate Garner]], cornerback [[Will Billingsley]], defensive end [[Ryan Baker (American football)|Ryan Baker]], guard [[Mark Lewis (offensive lineman)|Mark Lewis]], linebacker [[J. D. Folsom]] and wide receiver [[James Robinson (gridiron football)|James Robinson]].\n\n==Preseason==\n===Schedule===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"align=center\"\n|-\n! Week !! Date !! Opponent !! Result !! Record !! Game site !! NFL.com<br>recap\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n! 1\n| August 17\n| [[2009 Jacksonville Jaguars season|Jacksonville Jaguars]]\n| '''W''' 12\u20139\n| 1\u20130\n| [[Land Shark Stadium]]\n| [http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter?game_id=54739&season=2008&displayPage=tab_gamecenter Recap]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n! 2\n| August 22\n| [[2009 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]\n| '''W''' 27\u201317\n| 2\u20130\n| Land Shark Stadium \n| [http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter?game_id=54745&season=2008&displayPage=tab_gamecenter Recap]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n! 3\n| August 27\n| at [[2009 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]]\n| '''W''' 10\u20136\n| 3\u20130\n| [[Raymond James Stadium]]\n| [http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2009082750/2009/PRE3/dolphins@buccaneers Recap]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#cfc;\"\n! 4\n| September 3\n| at [[2009 New Orleans Saints season|New Orleans Saints]]\n| '''W''' 10\u20137\n| 4\u20130\n| [[Louisiana Superdome]]\n| [http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2009090359/2009/PRE4/dolphins@saints Recap]\n|}\n\n==Regular season==\n\n===Schedule===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"align=center\"\n|-\n! Week !! Date !! Opponent !! Result !! Record !! Game site !! NFL.com<br>recap\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fcc;\"\n! 1\n| September 13\n| at [[2009 Atlanta Falcons season|Atlanta Falcons]]\n| '''L''' 7\u201319\n| 0\u20131\n| [[Georgia Dome]]\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20121104113506/http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2009091300/2009/REG1/dolphins@falcons/recap Recap]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fcc;\"\n! 2\n| September 21\n| [[2009 Indianapolis Colts season|Indianapolis Colts]]\n| '''L''' 23\u201327