erguson]] NT <small>(IR)</small> [[Image:Injury icon.svg|7px]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">43</span> [[Ethan Kilmer]] FS <small>(Left Squad)</small>\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">14</span> ''[[Brennan Marion]]'' WR <small>(IR)</small> [[Image:Injury icon.svg|7px]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">76</span> ''[[Lydon Murtha]]'' OT <small>(IR)</small> [[Image:Injury icon.svg|7px]]\n{{NFLplayer|10|Chad Pennington|QB|IR}}\n\n|Practice Squad=\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">27</span> [[Will Billingsley]] CB <small>(Injured)</small> [[Image:Injury icon.svg|7px]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">20</span> ''[[Tristan Davis]]'' RB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">69</span> ''[[Ray Feinga]]'' G\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">89</span> ''[[Taurus Johnson]]'' WR\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">86</span> ''[[John Nalbone]]'' TE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">31</span> ''[[Nate Ness]]'' FS\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">11</span> ''[[Julius Pruitt]]'' WR\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20081216202722/http://www.miamidolphins.com/newsite/flash_content.asp Miami Dolphins Official Website]\n* [https://www.pro-football-reference.com/teams/mia/2009.htm 2009 Miami Dolphins season at Pro Football Reference]\n* [http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/teams/schedule?team=mia 2009 Miami Dolphins season at ESPN]\n\n{{Miami Dolphins}}\n{{Miami Dolphins seasons}}\n{{2009 NFL season by team}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2009 Miami Dolphins Season}}\n[[Category:2009 National Football League season by team|Miami]]\n[[Category:Miami Dolphins seasons]]\n[[Category:2009 in sports in Florida|Miami Dolphins]]\n", "name_user": "Wbm1058", "label": "safe", "comment": "Spelling correction; redirect bypass fromUniversity Of VirginiatoUniversity of Virginiausingpopups", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009_Miami_Dolphins_seas